Class main.WhiteCell

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.Cell
      • main.WhiteCell
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    main.Locatable

    public class main.WhiteCell
extends main.Cell
    An implementation of the abstract class cell. This class is controlled by an AI. It attacks all the sick cells. It also goes through mitosis, to make the game harder.

        public void findElement(java.awt.Graphics g,
                        int xOffset,
                        int yOffset)
        This method finds Sick cells and Viruses and represents the white cells' locating intelligence. It sets the cell to follow certain targets around, and also includes drifting motions to break up white cell groups. Curing sick cells are a priority, and then killing viruses.
        Parameters:
        g - the Graphics component for the canvas
        xOffset - the x fix for the canvas
        yOffset - the y fix for the canvas
